From 8931be366362363ff71ecb38406453634854751f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: JC Fillion-Robin <jcfr@nvidia.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Mar 2026 06:14:47 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add find_package(GXF) before holoscan in apps and operators

GXF is provided separately in OE (gxf-core). Add find_package(GXF 5.4.0
REQUIRED CONFIG) to all C++ applications and operators that use holoscan
so the GXF config is found from the sysroot before holoscan brings in
GXF targets.

Signed-off-by: JC Fillion-Robin <jcfr@nvidia.com>
---
 applications/endoscopy_out_of_body_detection/CMakeLists.txt      | 1 +
 applications/endoscopy_tool_tracking/cpp/CMakeLists.txt          | 1 +
 applications/multiai_endoscopy/cpp/post-proc-cpu/CMakeLists.txt  | 1 +
 .../multiai_endoscopy/cpp/post-proc-matx-cpu/CMakeLists.txt      | 1 +
 .../multiai_endoscopy/cpp/post-proc-matx-gpu/CMakeLists.txt      | 1 +
 applications/multiai_ultrasound/cpp/CMakeLists.txt               | 1 +
 .../operators/visualizer_icardio/CMakeLists.txt                  | 1 +
